Why this could be useful

1. Model comparison

You could compare AI systems based on their transformation skill profile.

Example:

Model	Map	Split	Lift	Invariant
Model A	strong	strong	weak	medium
Model B	medium	strong	strong	strong

This reveals cognitive strengths and weaknesses.

⸻

2. Training curriculum

The belt system naturally creates a training ladder.

Example progression:

White → Yellow → Green → Blue → Brown → Black

Each level adds new transformation complexity.

⸻

3. Alignment testing

Transformation tests can check if a system can:
	•	reflect on its reasoning
	•	detect contradictions
	•	preserve constraints
	•	recognize when analogies break

These are important safety signals.

